 confluent Kummer hypergeometric functions. We also\ninvestigate the radial solutions in the KN case in the regions near the event\nhorizon and far from the black hole. Finally, we construct several expansions\nof the solutions of the HE in terms of generalised hypergeometric functions of\nLauricella-Appell.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Feb 2016 21:00:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 27 Mar 2016 20:18:17 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 10 Jul 2016 16:01:57 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 13 Jul 2016 12:12:54 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Sun, 30 Oct 2016 10:26:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-01"}
