he sense that they are independent of the particular structure of the Gaussian\nHidden Markov Model (HMM) under consideration.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Feb 2016 05:23:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 4 Apr 2016 20:55:19 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 6 Jul 2016 16:29:28 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 26 Sep 2016 18:39:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-09-27"}
